The paper deals with image classification, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method is unsupervised, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of hyper-graphs and graph matching also suggests a connection to multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) fields.
